      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute benchmark in automotive preservation. This vehicle arrives in flawless condition, having been maintained to the highest possible standards of care. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, while the interior remains in impeccable, untouched state. Every component reflects a history of meticulous stewardship, offering the performance and aesthetic appeal of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that defies its age. Truly a collector-grade example that must be seen to be fully appreciated.",
