    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in absolutely stunning shape. It looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom; you won't find a more pristine example out there. Every curve is perfect, and the interior is spotless. Come by for a coffee and a chat\u2014I'd love to show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
