    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically peerless E92 M3, a final-run specimen of the high-revving S65 V8. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with a focus on long-term reliability; the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with BE Bearings and ARP hardware to mitigate clearance issues. The dual-clutch transmission (DCT) features a GTS software flash for optimized clamping pressure and lightning-fast shift maps. Handling is sharpened via a full suite of Turner Motorsport subframe bushings and Bilstein B16 adjustable dampers, ensuring the chassis is as communicative as it was on the assembly line. The induction note is enhanced by a carbon plenum, providing a visceral acoustic profile. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, ideal for the purist who understands the nuances of M-division engineering.",
      "price": 46850.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
